title: Expedition
alt: I'm pretty sure I've logged more hours in Google Maps over the past decade than in any game.
transcript:
[Cueball at a computer.]
February 4th:
Departed the mouth of the Lena River, heading south.
It has been nearly half an hour and still no sign of civilization.
The scroll wheel tempts me, but I will not cheat.Click click clickMy hobby: Getting lost on Google Maps satellite
